<p><FONT size=5 face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" color="#334455"><b><u>September 27, 2000.</u></b></FONT></p>

<p><FONT size=5 face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" color="#8b1a1a"><b>No News...</b></FONT><br>
