<ul>
<FONT size=3 face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" color="#8b1a1a"><p>I am really sorry to all those who have sent me stuff over the last 4 days. I havn't forgotten any of it, its all sitting in a pile on my desktop waiting for me to go through it.</p><p>Thing is, work has suddenly gotten really busy, so I cant update during the day (like I was before) and my evenings are being taken up working on the new monk quest. We finally are getting somewhere on it.</p><p>Anyways, I will catch up on the site later this week. In the meantime, please come over to the quest forum on the messageboards and help us crack this quest.</p></FONT></ul>

