<FONT size=3 face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" color="#8b1a1a"><p>I'm starting to work on the empty sections. I've made a start on the links section, but I would love people to send me more links, especially to other class sites. Credits section will be updated in a few minutes too.</p><p>But the Story and Editorial sections are sitting there bare, and I've had nothing to fill them with. Everyone has a favourite EQ story they love to tell. Write them down and send them to me <a href="mailto:zadkiel@monkly-business.com">here</a> (keep it clean please!)</p><p>And if anyone has any copies of the funny fake EQ logs (like the Veeshans Peak one, or the Cafe one, there have been lots of them) then please send them to me, I would love to put them up in the humour section</p></FONT></ul>
